quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  16,1,"Itegeko rya Allah (ryo kuza kw’imperuka) riregereje, bityo ntimuryihutishe. Ubutagatifu ni ubwe kandi ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamubangikanya nabyo"
  16,2,"Ku bw’itegeko rye, (Allah) amanura malayika (Gaburiheli) azanye ubutumwa k’uwo (Allah) ashaka mu bagaragu be (agira ati) \"Muburire (abantu) ko nta yindi mana (ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri) usibye njye; bityo nimuntinye"
  16,3,Yaremye ibirere n’isi ku mpamvu z’ukuri. Ubutagatifu ni ubwe kandi ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamubangikanya nabyo
  16,4,"Yeremye umuntu amukomoye mu ntanga, none uwo (muntu) yahisemo kuba umunyempaka ugaragara (mu guhakana izuka)"
  16,5,"(Allah) yanabaremeye amatungo; muri yo harimo ibibatera gususuruka (imyambaro) n’ibindi bibafitiye akamaro, ndetse hari n’ayo murya"
  16,6,Munashimishwa n’ubwiza bwayo igihe muyacyuye nimugoroba n’igihe muyahuye mu gitondo
  16,7,"Anikorera imitwaro yanyu iremereye akayijyana aho mutari gushobora kugera bitabagoye. Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wanyu ni Nyir’impuhwe zihebuje,Nyir’imbabazi"
  16,8,"(Yanaremye) ifarasi, icyimanyi (cy’ifarasi n’indogobe) ndetse n’indogobe; kugira ngo mubigendereho, kandi binababere imitako. Yanaremyen’ibindi bintu mutazi"
  16,9,"Allah ni we werekana inzira igororotse, ariko hari n’izindi zigoramye. Kandi iyo aza kubishaka yari kubayobora mwese"